      "title": "Pixomondo",
      "description": "Pixomondo is a multi-award-winning VFX and Virtual Production studio. We work with storytellers and production across film, TV or commercial for agile, creative solutions.",
      "text_excerpt": "Pixomondo\nWE ARE\nPIXOMONDO\nAn Oscar, BAFTA, and Emmy-winning force in creative innovation, proudly part of the Sony Pictures family. We’re not just making visual effects - we’re redefining how stories are made. By fusing artistry with next-gen technologies in real-time, and virtual production, we help filmmakers visualize, build worlds and bring ideas to life at scale. PXO is the partner for creators who want to push boundaries, challenge convention, and disrupt what comes next.\nCREATE.\nINSPIRE.\nDISRUPT.\nOUR SERVICES\n01. CREATIVE\nPXO\n, we provide integrated creative services that span the full production journey, bringing ideas to life from concept through final delivery. Our teams specialize in visualization (previs, techvis, postvis, and worldbuilding), all forms of virtual production with industry leading LED volumes and real-time toolsets, award-winning VFX, and expert on-set supervision to support filmmakers at every stage. With a future-focused approach, we develop and harness real-time workflows to accelerate creativity, enhance efficiency, and ensure technology always serves the story.\n02. CLARA\nPXO Clara\nis our dedicated virtual production division, delivering end-to-end support for filmmakers and studios worldwide. From LED design, commissioning, construction, and volume networking through to control operations, DMX/engine, DMZ integration, and on-set virtual production supervision, Clara provides the expertise to ensure every production runs seamlessly. With a focus on precision, reliability, and innovation, we help clients unlock the full potential of virtual production to tell their stories with creativity and confidence.\n03. INNOVATION\nPXO Innovation\nbrings together technologists, engineers, and creators to design and develop solutions that solve today’s production challenges and shape the future of filmmaking. Focused on delivering patented tools and workflows, the team empowers artists and storytellers through cutting-edge applications of real-time technology, gaussian splatting, and advanced engineering. By bridging R&D with production, PXO Innovation ensures Pixomondo stays at the forefront of creative technology, helping our clients achieve more ambitious, efficient, and imaginative storytelling.\n04. ACADEMY\nPXO Academy\nprovides advanced training programs and educational curricula in real-time technologies, virtual production and machine learning. With a focus on hands-on, practical learning, the Academy equips emerging talent with the tools and experience to thrive in a rapidly evolving industry. By preparing the next generation of digital storytellers, PXO Academy ensures a sustainable pipeline of skilled artists and technologists ready to push the boundaries of creative production.\nCurrent Partner:\nSeneca Polytechnic\n– Art Department Content Creation\nTogether, these four pillars form the foundation of PXO’s mission: to be a\ntrusted creative partner\n, integrating artistry, technology, and innovation to help storytellers bring"
    },
